author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Rosinter Restaurants To Open 8 Franchise Restaurants In Q1
text:
Feb 9 (Reuters) - ROSINTER RESTAURANTS:
* SAID ON THURSDAY IT WILL OPEN 8 FRANCHISE RESTAURANTS IN Q1
* SEES GROWTH OF ITS FRANCHISING NETWORK IN 2018 * AS OF END-2107 IT HAD 100 FRANCHISE RESTAURANTS Source text: bit.ly/2EQwDKy
